channel.title: Eleni - I guess its a remake?
channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/2h5388m.png[/img][/center]
[center]I see everyone making these remakes and I had the perfect base for a remake. So I guess here it is a remake?[/center]
[center][u]Quests[/u] Tutorial Island 20% Black Knight's Fortress 0% Cook's Assistant 80% Demon Slayer 0% Doric's Quest 0% Dragon Slayer 0% Ernest the Chicken 0% Goblin Diplomacy 0% Imp Catcher 0% The Knights Sword 0% Pirate's Treasure 0% Prince Ali Rescue 0% The Restless Ghost 0% Romeo & Juliet 0% Rune Mysteries 0% Sheep Shearer 0% Shield of Arrav 0% Vampire Slayer 0% Witch's Potion 0%
[u]Skills[/u] Agility Cooking Crafting Farming Firemaking Fishing Fletching Herblore Mining Prayer Runecrafting Slayer Smithing Thieving Woodcutting
[u]Combat[/u] Melee Magic Range
[u]Banking[/u] Bank Pin Input 1, 5, 10, All, X Withdraw 1, 5, 10, All, X Swap Insert Noting Item Saving Item Position Saving Deposit Box
[u]Trading[/u] Offer 1, 5, 10, All, X Remove 1, 5, 10, All, X Checking If Player Has Enough Room Confirm Screen Untradable Items
[u]Shopping[/u] Loading Items Refreshing Stock Sell 1, 5, 10, All, X Buy 1, 5, 10, All, X
[u]Emotes[/u] Preforming Emotes Skillcape Emotes
[u]Random Events[/u] Guardians Golem River Troll Tree Spirit Shade Zombie -[u]Gift Givers[/u] Certers Drill Demon Drunken Dwarf Freaky Forester Frog Genie Highwayman Jekyll and Hyde Lost Pirate Maze Mime Mysterious Old Man Pirate's Combination Lock Quiz Master Strange Box Strange Plant Security Guard Dangerous Ent Evil Chicken Exploding Rock Poison Gas Swarm Whirlpool -[u]Miscellaneous[/u] Evil Bob The Beekeeper Grab The Evil Twin Pinball Gravedigger Candlelight Pillory Prison Pete Sandwich Lady Lost & Found office
[u]Traveling/Teleporting [/u] Gnome Gliders Fairy Rings Canoeing Magic Carpets Mine Carts Eagles Hot Air Balloons Obelisks Grappling Shortcuts Teleporting Tablets Enchanted Jewelry Games Necklace Ring of Duelling Digsite Pendant Ring of Life Slayer Ring Amulet of Glory Bracelet of Combat Necklace of Skills
[size=12pt]I'll finish the list later i'm to lazy :p Also credits to thing1 on r-s for this list.[/size]
[size=14pt]Npc Dialogues:[/size] Currently Dialogues are being displayed randomly in this array But if I assign a dialogue for a certain NPC these will not show. [code] {"It's a rather beautiful day isn't it?"}, {"Sorry mate, I'm busy right now."}, {"I rather listen to funky dee than talk to you!"}, {"Conspiracy theory is true, yes sir."}, {"If I was dead right now, I wouldn't be here."},
{"Did you say something, oh nothing. Good."}, {"You better leave me alone before I go manic!"}, {"You talk to me, are you gonna bang doe?"}, {"Mate! You got nothing!"}, {"Better get them skills up, rather than down."},
{"I wish I had some headphones right now..."}, {"Memorize the state which isn't inconsequantial."}, {"You are the freaking terrorist here mate!"}, {"I'm the king of RuneScape, underground."}, {"Don't talk about stuff you don't know."},
{"Heroin, cocaine, crack, weed, blocks of hashes."}, {"Do you know how to pay the bills? F*ck off."}, {"Arrows don't come cheap. Especially runes."}, {"You better leave me alone before I call Ben."}, {"Talk to me again and you will be in trouble..."},
{"Hold tight man. You might slip! HAHAHA!"}, {"I'm not a man who is benevolent."},[/code]

[u]Welcome Screen[/u] Message Centre Membership Changes If You Become a Member Bank Pin Recovery Questions Message of the Week [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/20ii4a8.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/2vwgvnp.png[/img]
Credits to asshole_rule for this pic and his tutorial for brimhaven agility course. [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/2u53yut.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/fdr7o3.png[/img]
[u]Herblore[/u] Cleaning Unfinished Pots Finished Pots [IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/1z56per.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/oroznt.png[/img]
[size=24pt]Yes, I know this is a Project Insanity source, but I just had this on my desktop and I said what the heck. I will be moving to Hyperion or RuneSource. So I don't wanna see any flame about it being a PI.[/size][/center]
